    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "Well, I&#39;m dealing with legacy code and it would take a lot of when(...).thenReturn(...) statements to setup the mock just to prevent some NPE&#39;s and the like. On the other hand, a real object could be used safely for this. So it would be very handy to have an option to inject real objects along with mocks. Even if this may be a code smell, I consider it reasonable in this particular case."
