      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I was trying to inject Spring&#39;s own MockHttpServletRequest. Doing it with @Spy resulted in a my test subject getting a different mock than the one I&#39;d prepared in my test method. Using ReflectionTestUtils has the desired result."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 21945,
      "reputation" : 1777,
      "user_id" : 53732,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 58,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/hwYmk.jpg?s=256",
