    "score" : 17,
    "last_activity_date" : 1586285595,
    "creation_date" : 1586285595,
    "answer_id" : 61087329,
    "question_id" : 20270391,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In Spring there is a dedicated utility called <code>ReflectionTestUtils</code> for this purpose. Take the specific instance and inject into the the field.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>\n@Spy\n..\n@Mock\n..\n\n@InjectMock\nFoo foo;\n\n@BeforeEach\nvoid _before(){\n   ReflectionTestUtils.setField(foo,\"bar\", new BarImpl());// `bar` is private field\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
